      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WILDFIRE MISS (4) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Grade 5 three back before a placing at this track the following run. Has the ability and can find winning form this time. LITTLE KAOS (7) drifted back settling but did best work late to finish 4th at this track over 300m (18.11). Should be thereabouts. MULWEE PRINCESS (6) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (17.71) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Leading player again. JUST TOO EASY (2) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to bounce back.",
